.TH LPF-DIFF 8 "June 2026" "lpf 0.1.0-dev" "lpf Manual"
.SH NAME
lpf\-diff \- show the delta between current host state and a plan
.SH SYNOPSIS
lpf diff <policy>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Compare a generated plan with current lpf\-owned host state.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\-\-json
emit semantic diff as machine\-readable output
.SH EXAMPLES
lpf diff /etc/lpf.conf
.SH FILES
/etc/lpf.conf
/var/lib/lpf/history
/var/lib/lpf/rollback
.SH SAFETY NOTES
This command is read\-only.
.SH EXIT STATUS
0 on success.
Non\-zero when validation, planning, or host operations fail.
.SH SEE ALSO
lpf\-plan(8), lpf\-rules(8)
